OL,3,CDFDS cancels Jersey to Saint Malo
OL,4,Csailing
OL,6,FThe 6:55pm sailing between Jersey and
OL,7,FSaint Malo has been cancelled by DFDS
OL,8,Fafter the Tarifa Jet collided with the
OL,9,Fharbour ramp in St Helier earlier this
OL,10,Fevening (Sunday 29 March).
OL,12,FITV News understands that the incident
OL,13,Fcaused the vessel to lose its power.
OL,15,FIn a statement, DFDS says: "During
OL,16,FSunday evening's arrival into St
OL,17,FHelier harbour, Tarifa Jet made
OL,18,Fcontact with the ferry berth,
OL,19,Fresulting in some damage to the stern.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
