PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774897908
OL,3,CDFDS cancels Jersey to Saint Malo
OL,4,Csailing
OL,6,F"No passengers or crew were injured in
OL,7,Fthe incident.
OL,9,F"As a result, Sunday evening's sailing
OL,10,Fto St Malo has been cancelled, and we
OL,11,Fapologise to passengers for the
OL,12,Finconvenience caused.
OL,14,F"DFDS officials are working with port
OL,15,Fauthorities and carrying out an
OL,16,Finspection of the vessel."
OL,18,FThe ferry company adds that a further
OL,19,Fupdate will be provided tomorrow
OL,20,F(Monday 30 March).
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
