OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774897908
OL,3,CDFDS cancels Jersey to Saint Malo
OL,4,Csailing
OL,6,FA spokesperson from Ports of Jersey
OL,7,Fadds: "No injuries have been reported.
OL,8,FWe are currently undertaking
OL,9,Finspections of both the operator
OL,10,Fvessel and harbour infrastructure.
OL,12,F"An investigation will take place with
OL,13,Fthe operator and the vessel's flag
OL,14,Fstate to understand the cause of the
OL,15,Fincident."
